                        <interp inst="t18410510-name-92" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>GEORGE KEDGE</persName>
                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> These duplicates relate to part of the property pawned by the prisoner Henry.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">HENRY ALLSHORNE—
